## Sources

- XutaxKamay PR #384 on corna/me_cleaner — initial ME 15/16 research
- Intel 600-series PCH Datasheet Vol1, Doc 648364 — ADL HAP location confirmed
- Intel 700-series PCH Datasheet Vol1, Doc 743835 — RPL HAP location confirmed
- Intel 400-series PCH Datasheet (ICL On-Package), Doc 615170 — ICL HAP confirmed
- Community reverse engineering via me_cleaner issues and coreboot mailing list
- Hardware confirmation of ME 12/14 by this repo
